   - Paid services or commercial events
   - Any activity where the primary purpose is commercial gain

2. PROHIBITED USERS

   The following entities may NOT use this software:
   - Advertising agencies
   - Marketing companies
   - Event promotion agencies
   - "Guerrilla marketing" practitioners
